{"tid":1841254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"芬航禁員工戴口罩 網民轟罔顧健康促罷搭","createTime":"2020-01-25T08:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T11:59:48.000Z","uid":60868,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6e5b921d62cf6d7d1c643c2c9ee3463e158719be","tid":1841254,"uid":60868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:02:12.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】芬航禁員工戴口罩 網民轟罔顧健康促罷搭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐全球，本港多間航空公司先後放寬規定，容許機組人員執勤時戴口罩，惟獨芬蘭航空（芬航）唱反調。《蘋果》接獲多名芬航空中服務員投訴，指在日益嚴峻的疫情下，公司昨日竟發內部通告，重申禁止機組人員執勤時戴口罩，批評芬航罔顧員工和乘客安全，「唔覺意瀨咗嘢，真係一鑊熟。」<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200124&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60521696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200124%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60521696&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FSbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=3f0f1b15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200124%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60521696&h=8de1b94d\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200124&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60521696</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea25a8e6134efc98bd4e5c0016cc5c9e535172ae","tid":1841254,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:04:33.000Z","msg":"推 罷搭"},{"pid":"b436eac2c19b153b9abc04179aeed565c93f1d8b","tid":1841254,"uid":60868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},